{"id":"351784765_QUAREP-LiMi_a_community_endeavor_to_advance_quality_assessment_and_reproducibility_in_light_microscopy","abstract":"The community-driven initiative Quality Assessment and Reproducibility for Instruments & Images in Light Microscopy (QUAREP-LiMi) wants to improve reproducibility for light microscopy image data through quality control (QC) management of instruments and images. It aims for a common set of QC guidelines for hardware calibration and image acquisition, management and analysis.","authors":["Ulrike Boehm","Glyn Nelson","Claire M Brown","Steve Bagley"],"meta":["May 2021Nature Methods 18(12)","DOI:10.1038/s41592-021-01162-y"],"references":["343922705_Antibody_validation_for_protein_expression_on_tissue_slides_a_protocol_for_immunohistochemistry","341813270_Is_the_reproducibility_crisis_fuelling_poor_mental_health_in_science","332159306_FAIRsharing_as_a_community_approach_to_standards_repositories_and_policies","323243757_Artificial_intelligence_faces_reproducibility_crisis","260150243_Discovery_of_HeLa_Cell_Contamination_in_HES_Cells_Call_for_Cell_Line_Authentication_in_Reproductive_Biology_Research","42832531_Antibody_validation","338058725_This_AI_researcher_is_trying_to_ward_off_a_reproducibility_crisis","329256811_To_Read_More_Papers_or_to_Read_Papers_Better_A_Crucial_Point_for_the_Reproducibility_Crisis","324758435_Reproducibility_crisis_in_science_or_unrealistic_expectations","324511312_Identity_Crisis_-_Rigor_and_Reproducibility_in_Human_Cell_Lines","323712925_Opinion_Is_science_really_facing_a_reproducibility_crisis_and_do_we_need_it_to","322851358_Public_archives_for_biological_image_data","277409383_Reproducibility_Changing_the_policies_and_culture_of_cell_line_authentication","277083953_Reproducibility_crisis_Blame_it_on_the_antibodies","275053775_A_resource_for_cell_line_authentication_annotation_and_quality_control","261997384_Cell-line_authentication_demystified"]}